snippet.title: Get Packed | Launch Trailer | First on Stadia
snippet.description:
Get Packed is *OUT NOW* on Stadia! Join the Last Ditch Removals company in this frantic couch co-op party game, full of calamity and physics-based co-op carnage with your friends.
